<div style="position:absolute;left:38.40px;top:616.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">1.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:616.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">1)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:94.80px;top:616.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">…</span><span class="cls_007">例</span><span class="cls_008">：  </span><span class="cls_007">はい、歌えます。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:110.40px;top:632.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">れい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:150.00px;top:632.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ほん</span></div>
